valent to the peakons. Solving the parametric representation of solution on\nthe symplectic submanifold gives a class of new algebro-geometric solution of\nthe CH equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2002 17:12:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2002 21:43:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2002 18:29:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-08"}
